Fulham are signing Hellas Verona goalkeeper Nikolai Mihailov.

The 26-year-old is the son of former Bulgaria goalkeeper Boris Mihailov who played for Reading.

Fulham have held an interest in the Verona keeper since last year when his former club Liverpool were also linked with a return bid. 

