Fulham have held talks with free agent Timo Hildebrand but hope to agree a loan for Mihailov with a view to a permanent £400,000 deal.

Coach Felix Magath has put faith in a young squad but is under increasing pressure at Fulham after a poor start to the Championship season.

Tim Sherwood and former Celtic boss Neil Lennon are understood to be under consideration should Fulham make another managerial change. 

